{"tid":1783060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有無人已經買左機票18號去釜山支持港隊","createTime":"2019-12-14T13:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T13:58:32.000Z","uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1df9770b93e96ab358a380c18e001994f661506d","tid":1783060,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:09:08.000Z","msg":"【售票詳情】 &mdash; 香港出戰 2019東亞足球錦標賽&mdash;決賽週<br />\n<br />\n想遠赴韓國支持香港隊嘅球迷要留意啦，喺韓國釜山舉行嘅2019東亞足球錦標賽&mdash;決賽週賽事今日開始賣飛啦。<br />\n<br />\n想買飛嘅球迷可以去到interpark選購：<a href=\"http://ticket.interpark.com/Contents/Promotion/Event/EAFFE1?Language=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fticket.interpark.com%2FContents%2FPromotion%2FEvent%2FEAFFE1%3FLanguage%3Den&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWtRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=6183d59f\" target=\"_blank\">http://ticket.interpark.com/Contents/Promotion/Event/EAFFE1?Language=en</a><br />\n<br />\n=============================<br />\n香港隊比賽詳請<br />\n<br />\n韓國 對 香港<br />\n日期 : 12 月 11 日<br />\n開賽時間 : 晚上 7 時 30 分 (當地時間)<br />\n地點 : Busan Asiad Main Stadium<br />\n<br />\n日本 對 香港<br />\n日期 : 12 月 14 日<br />\n開賽時間 : 晚上 7 時 30 分 (當地時間)<br />\n地點 : Busan Gudeok Stadium<br />\n<br />\n香港 對 中國<br />\n日期 : 12 月 18 日<br />\n開賽時間 :下午 4 時 15 分 (當地時間)<br />\n地點 : Busan Asiad Main Stadium<br />\n<br />\n******************************************<br />\n由於是次比賽不設球迷區，經過同本地球迷組織協調過後，建議想一齊打氣嘅球迷可以買以下區域：<br />\n<br />\n12.11 對 韓國 | Busan Asiad Stadium | 全場劃位 - 買Category 2 - S08 (KRW 30,000)<br />\n12.14 對 日本 | Gudeok Stadium | 沒有劃位 - Category 2 (KRW 20,000)<br />\n12.18 對 中國 | Busan Asiad Stadium | 全場劃位 - 買Category 2 - N26 (KRW 30,000)<br />\n<br />\n***所有門票手續費+KRW 2,000<br />\n<br />\n#HongKong #香港勁揪 #東亞盃決賽週 #EAFF2019 #香港隊 #中日韓 #OnTour<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">東亞足球錦標賽決賽今天在韓國開踢，按日程12月18日將上演中國隊對陣香港隊。賽前布陣緊張，網傳不僅球隊緊張，外圍也緊張，原因或是中港足球比賽忽然加入政治意味，成為雙方大戰。中國隊或受壓力政治任務是必須贏，香港隊則受到港民熱捧希望戰勝中國隊，以煥發反送中意氣。香港人醞釀多購票前往韓國助威。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"21cd4c4880849a3e802f00e563dfaafb5fade7fc","tid":1783060,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:14:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zrNpRn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzrNpRn5.jpg&h=7453738e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Hhk89N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Hhk89N.jpg&h=e421777a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FPC5APO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFPC5APO.jpg&h=08184019&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcff55ea2d75795ba9e125512b6408972d71a229","tid":1783060,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06da2ca0c7b3beafbafa61328b1b150cc8f163be","tid":1783060,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0908c5b1617fc7a0ced702aca3f898f8efc6cfa5","tid":1783060,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"聽日有社福集會阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpk64Ys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqpk64Ys.jpg&h=9c03902a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}